data.name: CopyToDSLiveButton.ToolTip
data.value:
Makes a copy of the Symbol Tables in their current state, including all Variables, Parameters, and Functions. These are then loaded into a new DSLive Session, wherein expressions can be evaluated, and functions can be run as you please.
Changes made in the DSLive session ARE NOT re-applied to the running Program.
Just like calling "Debug_StartDSLiveSessionFromCurrentExecutionState()".
